29127.title: MTV Unplugged: Liam Gallagher
29127.description: Recorded live at the Hull City Hall, legendary frontman Liam Gallagher performs a one-off acoustic set of songs from his solo albums along with some Oasis classics, exclusively for MTV Unplugged.
